dialogue.text: Jenny Wakeman. Again, you come to intercept me. You can’t cause any change this time! I have already begun my plan-
No time for me to hear about your PLAN. I want revenge on that blue haired jerk back on Earth!
Huh? You make no sense, Wakeman.
I want to battle a different way this time. With the power of singing.
That’s laughable, what do you think this will achieve?
If it can stop me, it can stop you.
Very well. I’ll play this childish game of yours, I am guaranteed to win regardless.
